+    begin
+        // [FEATURE] [BOM Cost Share] [Production BOM]
+        // [SCENARIO] Rolled-up Capacity Cost for a component with blank Production BOM should be the same as for a component with no Production BOM.
+        // [GIVEN] A blank Production BOM has no lines, so it effectively means the component has no BOM structure.
